name: BananianX
tagline: Here is a script, which installs GUI on bananian.
body:
### Welcome to BananianX
I have created a Skript, which installs GUI on the Banana Pi. Bananian was made for the Banana Pi as Server, so you donÂ´t really need a GUI. But some people would like to have a GUI, so I have made this Skript.
